# Production Operations

This app is **live in production on Railway**. The `DATABASE_URL` in `.env` points to the production database. You have access to the Railway environment via the Railway CLI.

## Git Discipline

- NEVER commit or push unless the user explicitly asks you to.

## Database Safety

- Schema lives at `src/lib/db/schema.ts` (Drizzle ORM).
- Use `drizzle-kit push` for incremental schema changes. NEVER use `drizzle-kit migrate` or `drizzle-kit generate`.
- Only make **additive** changes: new tables, new columns with sensible defaults, new indexes.
- NEVER drop columns, rename columns, drop tables, or alter types unless the user explicitly approves.
- Before pushing schema changes, review the Drizzle push preview and confirm no data loss will occur.
